videos.description: USC's Chimezie Metu misses an easy dunk in transition.
videos.headline: USC misses easy dunk opportunity

videos.description: Cal's Ivan Rabb dunks it hard off the missed jumper, almost knocking down the stanchion.
videos.headline: Ivan Rabb tries to break the rim on the dunk

videos.description: In the first half against Cal, USC's De'Anthony Melton gets the ball in transition and is pushed to the court by Cal's Don Coleman.
videos.headline: USC's Melton gets knocked to ground on hard foul

videos.description: Jordan McLaughlin banks in a half-court buzzer-beater to even USC up with California at halftime.
videos.headline: McLaughlin hits half-court buzzer-beater for USC

videos.description: USC Trojans' football team shows their fans the Rose Bowl Trophy during halftime.
videos.headline: USC's football team shows off the Rose Bowl trophy at halftime

videos.description: Cal's Kingsley Okoroh with the easy dunk as Ivan Rabb draws the attention of the defense.
videos.headline: Cal's Okoroh dunks under the basket

videos.description: Cal's Ivan Rabb throws down the monster dunk off the alley-oop and the USC bench goes crazy.
videos.headline: Rabb throws down off the alley-oop

videos.description: USC's Chimezie Metu makes up for the earlier missed dunk by throwing down the dunk off the alley-oop.
videos.headline: USC's Metu dunks off the alley-oop

videos.description: Cal's Ivan Rabb gets a big block and the Golden Bears' good ball movement leads to a 3 pointer.
videos.headline: Cal turns defense into 3 points

videos.description: After a missed free throw from USC's Jordan McLaughlin, the Trojans keep the ball on their side of the court, but Cal's Jabari Bird soars for the big block.
videos.headline: Cal's defense comes up big with a block with under 30 seconds remaining

videos.description: USC's Jordan McLaughlin keeps the ball and drives to the basket to give the Trojans a late lead.
videos.headline: USC hits clutch layup

videos.description: With 5.2 seconds left and USC down a point, Jordan McLaughlin drives into the paint for a layup, but gets blocked by Cal's Ivan Rabb to preserve a 74-73 victory.
videos.headline: Cal wins on last-second block at the rim

videos.description: California's Ivan Rabb discusses the big block against USC to seal the game for the Golden Bears.
videos.headline: CAL's Ivan Rabb talks about big block to end the game
